# Rebuild permission

The user has given **full permission to rebuild the app whenever it is required**.

- After making changes that affect the built output (e.g. source, config, nginx), run `npm run build` without asking.
- If deployment or serving depends on a fresh build, run the build as part of the change.
- No need to ask for confirmation before running `npm run build`.
